1. Cover/Header Image

A wide banner behind the avatar. Users can upload/change the cover for personalization.

2. Friends/Connections List

Display a horizontal scroll of profile avatars (friends, followers, or teammates).

3. Achievements/Badges Gallery

More visual display of earned badgesâ€”grid with icons, dates, and expandable details.

4. Skill Tags/Interests

Tag chips showing user skills, interests, or expertise; users can add/remove them.

5. Activity Feed with Media

Timeline supports images, videos, links, and reactions (like, comment, share).

6. Progress Bars

Show goals, learning progress, or stats visually (e.g., profile completeness, coding streak).

7. Custom Themes

Let users pick accent colors or gradients for their profile page.

8. Notifications Area

Show recent alerts, messages, or requests with a bell icon and dropdown.

9. Recent Projects/Portfolio

Card/grid of recent work, featured posts, or portfolio items.

10. Settings Drawer/Panel

Quick settings for privacy, notification preferences, account management.

11. In-app Messaging/Chat

Direct messaging or quick chat with connections.

12. Social Sharing

Share profile or posts directly to other social platforms.

13. Editable Custom Fields

Favorite quote, location, birthday, website, or links.

14. QR Code/Download Profile

QR code for sharing profile; download profile as vCard or PDF.

15. Accessibility Features

Font size toggle, color theme for colorblind support, keyboard navigation.